20
00:01:33,158 --> 00:01:35,319
...tentang kemampuanku?

21
00:01:54,817 --> 00:01:56,232
Sudah kubilang...

22
00:01:56,947 --> 00:01:59,513
...aku sudah tahu...

23
00:02:01,658 --> 00:02:03,910
...setiap tempat persembunyianmu.

